Package com.asemantics.rdfcoder.model.ontology

This package defines a basic ontology validator.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Ontology
    Defines the ontology generated by a JavaCodeHandler
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseOntology
    Defines ontology predicates common to every Ontology.
    DefaultOntology
    Default implementation of Ontology interface.
    Ontology.ListBounds
    Declares the restriction bounds for an array.
    ValidatingCodeModel
    This decorator validates addition of model triples over a given ontology.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    OntologyException
    Defines any exception related to ontology validation.
